trans-unit.source: Gets the time the copy operation completed, and indicates whether completion was due to a successful copy, the cancelling of the operation, or a failure.
trans-unit.target: Gets the time the copy operation completed, and indicates whether completion was due to a successful copy, the cancelling of the operation, or a failure.

trans-unit.source: A <codeEntityReference>T:System.DateTimeOffset</codeEntityReference> containing the completion time, or <codeInline>null</codeInline> if the operation has not completed.
